{
  "texts": [
    "The response format for Reasoners will be \"Decision: 0/1\", while it is \"Analysis: XXX\" for Guides and Validator.",
    "For Reasoners, Guides, and Validator, the prompt includes 3-4 examples encompassing user content alongside corresponding system responses that adhere to the specified format.",
    "The examples for Response Analyzer is slightly different and illustrated in Section 5.2.",
    "We set the temperature as 0.7 in the LLMs to achieve varied rephrasings of the questions while maintaining certain constraints.",
    "The same prompt and hyperparameters are used for different LLMs."
  ]
}